  <entry>
    <author>
      <name>binq</name>
    </author>
    <category term="认知成长" scheme="https://binq200108.github.io/categories/growth/"/>
    <category term="思维模型" scheme="https://binq200108.github.io/tags/%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/"/>
    <category term="第一性原理" scheme="https://binq200108.github.io/tags/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%80%A7%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86/"/>
    <category term="独立思考" scheme="https://binq200108.github.io/tags/%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/"/>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<p>第一性原理是最强大的思维工具之一，它要求我们回到事物最基本的真理，从那里开始推理。这种思维方式帮助我们跳出经验主义的局限，找到问题的本质。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="什么是第一性原理"><a href="#什么是第一性原理" class="headerlink" title="什么是第一性原理"></a>什么是第一性原理</h2><p>亚里士多德将第一性原理定义为”认识事物的第一基础”。在实践中，它意味着：</p><ul><li><strong>不依赖类比推理</strong> — “别人怎么做”不是你应该怎么做的理由</li><li><strong>分解到最基本的事实</strong> — 什么是你确定为真的？</li><li><strong>从基本事实重新构建</strong> — 基于这些事实，逻辑上应该怎么做？</li></ul><p>类比思维是一种捷径：看到别人做了什么，我们也照着做。这在大多数时候是高效的，但它的局限在于——你永远无法通过模仿超越被模仿者。</p><p><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1462331940025-496dfbfc7564?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80" alt="宇宙中的基本法则，是一切复杂现象背后的简单规律" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></p><div class="img-caption">宇宙中的基本法则，是一切复杂现象背后的简单规律</div><p>万物运行的底层，是极其简洁的规律。从牛顿三大定律到热力学定律，从量子力学到相对论，每一次物理学的重大突破，都是回到第一性原理的结果。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-single portrait">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="仰望山峰 — 回到本质需要勇气"      data-camera="SONY XXXX-XX"      data-lens="FE 28mm F2.3 GM"      data-iso="100"      data-focal="32mm"      data-aperture="ƒ4"      data-shutter="1/160s"      data-location="深圳·XXX山" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>回到本质需要仰望的勇气，也需要俯身的耐心</figcaption></figure><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="live-photo" data-live-video="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/timerring/scratchpad2023/2024/2025-05-16-15-48-05.mp4">    <img class="live-photo-image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80" alt="海面与夕光的实况瞬间">    <video class="live-photo-video" playsinline preload="metadata"></video>    <button class="live-photo-toggle" type="button" aria-label="播放实况" aria-pressed="false">实况</button>  </div>  <figcaption>实况图示例：左上角实况图标；桌面端悬停自动播放，移动端点图标播放；点击图片可像普通图片一样进入预览</figcaption></figure><h2 id="投资中的第一性原理"><a href="#投资中的第一性原理" class="headerlink" title="投资中的第一性原理"></a>投资中的第一性原理</h2><p>投资的第一性原理是什么？</p><blockquote><p>一家公司的价值 &#x3D; 其未来所有现金流的折现值。</p></blockquote><p>这意味着：</p><ul><li>股价短期是投票机，长期是称重机</li><li>你需要理解的是企业的本质，而不是市场的情绪</li><li>估值必须基于对未来现金流的合理预估</li></ul><div class="table-wrap"><table><thead><tr><th>思维方式</th><th>特点</th><th>适用场景</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>类比推理</td><td>快速、基于经验</td><td>日常决策、低风险情况</td></tr><tr><td>第一性原理</td><td>深入、基于事实</td><td>重大决策、创新突破</td></tr><tr><td>归纳推理</td><td>从特殊到一般</td><td>发现规律、建立理论</td></tr><tr><td>演绎推理</td><td>从一般到特殊</td><td>验证假设、逻辑论证</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>巴菲特和芒格之所以成功，正是因为他们始终回到这个最基本的原则。当市场恐慌时，他们不看股价走势图，而是计算企业的内在价值。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-ratio r-43-34">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611974789855-9c2a0a7236a3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="市场数据分析"      data-camera="Nikon Z8"      data-lens="NIKKOR Z 24-70mm f/2.8 S"      data-iso="400"      data-focal="42mm"      data-aperture="ƒ5.6"      data-shutter="1/500s"      data-location="东京·丸之内" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="财务计算"      data-camera="Canon EOS R5"      data-lens="RF 50mm F1.2L USM"      data-iso="200"      data-focal="50mm"      data-aperture="ƒ2.8"      data-shutter="1/250s"      data-location="上海·陆家嘴" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>4:3 横图 + 3:4 竖图 — 市场分析与深度计算</figcaption></figure><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-ratio r-34-43">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="数据细节" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="数据大盘" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>3:4 竖图 + 4:3 横图 — 从微观细节到宏观全局</figcaption></figure><h2 id="自然界的第一性原理"><a href="#自然界的第一性原理" class="headerlink" title="自然界的第一性原理"></a>自然界的第一性原理</h2><p>自然界是第一性原理最好的老师。万物的复杂表象之下，隐藏着简洁的基本规律——物理定律、数学结构、进化法则。从雪花的六角对称到银河的螺旋臂，从 DNA 的双螺旋到蜂巢的正六边形，同样的基本原理反复塑造着这个世界。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-grid col-3">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1635070041078-e363dbe005cb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="数学公式" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509228468518-180dd4864904?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="几何结构" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501594907352-04cda38ebc29?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="光与能量" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>一排三图 — 数学、几何与能量，自然界最基本的语言</figcaption></figure><p>从宏观到微观，自然的秩序无处不在。海岸线的分形、树木的分支、河流的网络——它们都遵循着相同的基本模式。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-grid col-4">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="森林" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470071459604-3b5ec3a7fe05?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="山谷" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470252649378-9c29740c9fa8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="田野" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472214103451-9374bd1c798e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="日落" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>一排四图 — 森林、山谷、田野、日落，自然的四种面貌</figcaption></figure><h2 id="从分解到重构"><a href="#从分解到重构" class="headerlink" title="从分解到重构"></a>从分解到重构</h2><p>第一性原理的实践可以分为两个阶段：<strong>分解</strong>和<strong>重构</strong>。</p><p><strong>分解</strong>是将复杂问题拆解到不可再分的基本事实。就像拆解一台机器，直到你看到每一个零件的本来面目。</p><p><strong>重构</strong>是基于这些基本事实，重新组合出解决方案。这个过程往往能产生颠覆性的创新，因为你不受既有方案的束缚。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-ratio r-32-23">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487058792275-0ad4aaf24ca7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="代码逻辑" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="电路板" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>3:2 横图 + 2:3 竖图 — 软件的逻辑与硬件的结构</figcaption></figure><p>Elon Musk 在 SpaceX 的实践就是经典案例。当所有人都说火箭发射太贵时，他没有接受这个”常识”，而是回到第一性原理：火箭的原材料成本是多少？铝合金、碳纤维、钛合金——这些材料的成本只占火箭售价的 2%。于是他决定自己造火箭。</p><p>用同样的思维方式，我们可以从第一性原理出发估算企业的内在价值：</p><section class="cg-code-shell"><div class="cg-code-head"><span class="cg-code-file"><svg class="cg-code-file-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg><span class="cg-code-title" title="snippet.python">snippet.python</span></span><button class="cg-code-copy" type="button" aria-label="复制代码"><svg class="cg-copy-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 16H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v2m-6 12h8a2 2 0 002-2v-8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-8a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg></button></div><div class="cg-code-body"><div class="cg-code-scroll"><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 简单的内在价值估算 (DCF 模型)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">intrinsic_value</span>(<span class="params">fcf, growth_rate, discount_rate, years=<span class="number">10</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    fcf: 自由现金流 (亿元)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    growth_rate: 预期增长率</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    discount_rate: 折现率</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    value = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> year <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, years + <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        future_cf = fcf * (<span class="number">1</span> + growth_rate) ** year</span><br><span class="line">        value += future_cf / (<span class="number">1</span> + discount_rate) ** year</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 终值: 永续增长模型 (假设长期增长率 3%)</span></span><br><span class="line">    terminal_growth = <span class="number">0.03</span></span><br><span class="line">    terminal_value = (fcf * (<span class="number">1</span> + growth_rate) ** years * (<span class="number">1</span> + terminal_growth)) \</span><br><span class="line">                     / (discount_rate - terminal_growth)</span><br><span class="line">    value += terminal_value / (<span class="number">1</span> + discount_rate) ** years</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">round</span>(value, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 示例: FCF=100亿, 增长率8%, 折现率10%</span></span><br><span class="line">result = intrinsic_value(<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">0.08</span>, <span class="number">0.10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;内在价值估算: <span class="subst">&#123;result&#125;</span> 亿元&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="cg-code-fade" aria-hidden="true"></div></div><div class="cg-code-toggle-row"><button class="cg-code-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="展开代码块"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></button></div></section><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-ratio r-23-32">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1473448912268-2022ce9509d8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="森林小径" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="雪山全景" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">  </div>  <figcaption>2:3 竖图 + 3:2 横图 — 窄径通向广阔</figcaption></figure><h2 id="拼贴与组合"><a href="#拼贴与组合" class="headerlink" title="拼贴与组合"></a>拼贴与组合</h2><p>理解了分解与重构，就能看到事物之间隐藏的关联——看似不相关的领域，往往共享相同的底层原理。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-mosaic">    <div class="mosaic-stack">      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526374965328-7f61d4dc18c5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="数据流" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="协作空间" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    </div>    <div class="mosaic-full">      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1456406644174-8ddd4cd52a06?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="纵深结构" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    </div>  </div>  <figcaption>拼贴布局 — 左2小 + 右1大，数据、协作与纵深</figcaption></figure><h2 id="如何练习"><a href="#如何练习" class="headerlink" title="如何练习"></a>如何练习</h2><p>第一性原理不是天赋，而是一种可以训练的思维习惯。</p><ol><li>面对一个问题，先问”为什么”</li><li>对每个回答继续追问”为什么”</li><li>直到你到达不可再分的基本事实</li><li>从这些事实出发，重新构建你的理解</li></ol><p>关键在于保持好奇心，拒绝”大家都是这么做的”这类回答。每一次你选择追问本质而非接受惯例，都是在强化这种思维模式。</p><figure class="photo-figure">  <div class="photo-flex">    <div class="wide">      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519681393784-d120267933ba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="星空下的雪山" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    </div>    <div class="narrow">      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="湖光山色" class="cg-lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async">    </div>  </div>  <figcaption>宽窄组合 — 广角视野与聚焦一隅</figcaption></figure><h2 id="写在最后"><a href="#写在最后" class="headerlink" title="写在最后"></a>写在最后</h2><p>第一性原理不是要你否定一切经验，而是在关键决策时，有能力回到最本质的层面去思考。它与类比思维并不矛盾——日常小事用类比提高效率，重大决策用第一性原理确保方向正确。</p><p>正如费曼所说：”我不能创造的东西，我就不理解。”真正的理解，始于第一性原理。test</p>]]>
